title: The imaginary Trump piñata at the Hispanic Caucus banquet
text: Rep. Linda Sánchez was kidding when she told the 2,100 or so guests at the Congressional Hispanic Caucus Institute’s awards banquet Thursday night: " After the program, the Donald Trump piñata will be set up in that corner. " But the California Democrat captured the spirit of many of the quips and digs at the annual fundraising […] ...
